  "content_html": "<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:40px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Smart parking</span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">The IGP smart parking system makes use of advanced computer vision technology in order to identify vacant parking or occupied parking and then correspondingly turns on an appropriate green/red/blue signal of vacant or occupied parking.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">The system includes the option of up to 2 cameras which enable the identification of up to 3 parking lots in one unit.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></p>\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:18px;\">\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Marking free/occupied parking spaces using red/green/blue LED lights.</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Extremely reliable technology for identifying the condition of the parking space using a camera (not ultrasonic)</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Identification of car numbers.</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Finding the location of a car in the parking lot.</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Safety - very low voltage feed.</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Communication Rs485, TCP/IP</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Monitoring of 2 parking spaces per unit.</span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"> </p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Options:</span></span></p>\n<ul class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:18px;\">\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Signage and guidance system based on 32' screens</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">An alarm report for maintenance purposes that includes the possibility of communication alarms and unit faults.</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Production of a monthly report with a daily breakdown regarding the amount of uses in the parking lots in the building.</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Production of a daily graph that includes a parking lot usage profile by time of day</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Displaying data in real time on AutoCAD images of the parking lot.</span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:40px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Related products</span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Control Applications Ltd</span><